CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, May 14, 1966, pg. 1A, reads: "Breakthrough - Stage star Eartha Kitt was on hand in Hill District last week to held citizens launch a massive 'self help' drive to renew the community. On exhibition was a remodeled slum home.  Effort is sponsored by Citizens Committee on Hill District Renewal.  Eartha was appearing in city in presentation of stage play 'Owl and Pussycat.'  - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Eartha Kitt surrounded by crowd for "self help" drive promotion by Citizens Committee on Hill District Renewal, at Colwell and Vine Streets, Hill District
